body {
margin: 0;

.container {

h1 {

list-style-type: disc;

padding-left: 30%;

@keyframes fadeIn {
from { opacity: 0; }
to { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes slideDown {
from { transform: translateY(-30px); opacity: 0; }
to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes popIn {
0% { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 0; }
100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
}
</style>
